{"tid":1987960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港治療藥方清單","createTime":"2020-04-25T00:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T04:10:56.000Z","uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8728c326d35b61fce64bce47795b39d5ad64c3e2","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:35:58.000Z","msg":"藥方就係大家要食「團結」同埋「尊重」藥丸<br />\n如果大家唔食既話<br />\n我相信香港會死係自己人身上<br />\n所以往後既道路<br />\n大家諗清楚係咪不分化 不割席<br />\n即使核爆係咪都同大家齊上齊落呢？<br />\n所以任何民主派會唔會降低「底線」呢？<br />\n默默支持前線手足同提供support比佢地<br />\n但我同意要互相檢討同埋達成共識<br />\n如果自問自己做唔到既話<br />\n就唔好做同路人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b954775b7d9bc55bc39cd4a59a3c5279f8fe65","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9f9b7044119aae133943011ffedfedbe25ee2d","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T00:44:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b255cc2689f441757fda46aa7ad69d4fc92a957","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"707eb378303fb713fdbc519ee7eb937686021488","tid":1987960,"uid":226612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c25bfec5d6d564afad554ecfa7e1d64102efd5d0","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1c4aad510af7d3005805a4fa3883c09378af1758","tid":1987960,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}